'''Jeyne Poole''' is a background character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. She is played by an unidentified extra and only appears in the [[Winter is Coming (episode)|series premiere]]. Jeyne Poole is a friend of [[Sansa Stark]] and daughter of [[Vayon Poole]], the Steward of [[Winterfell]].

